ver South-West]]\n** [[Neigette River (Les Basques)|Neigette River]]\n* [[Bic River]]\n** [[Aulnes River (Bic River tributary)|Aulnes River]]\n** [[Gamache River (Rimouski-Neigette)|Gamache River]]\n* [[H\u00e2t\u00e9e River]]\n** [[Branche de la rivi\u00e8re H\u00e2t\u00e9e]]\n}}\n\n=== Watershed of Rimouski River and Eastern tributaries ===\n* [[Rimouski River]]\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n'''West bank''' (from confluence)\n* [[Rigoumabe River]]\n* [[Little Rimouski River]]\n** [[Rivi\u00e8re des Accores]]\n** [[Rivi\u00e8re Plate (petite Rivi\u00e8re Rimouski)|Rivi\u00e8re Plate]] (Flat River (Little Rimouski River))\n* [[Noire River (Rimouski River tributary)|Noire River]]\n* [[Blanche River (Rimouski River tributary)|Blanche River]]\n* [[Little Touradi River]]\n* [[France River]]\n* [[Boucher River (Rimouski River tributary)|Boucher River]]\n* [[Grand Touradi River]]\n** [[Brisson River (Grand Touradi River tributary)|Brisson River]]\n** [[Cennelier River]]\n\n'''East bank''' (from upper part)\n* [[Br\u00fbl\u00e9 River]]\n* [[Bois Br\u00fbl\u00e9 River]]\n* [[Macp\u00e8s River]]\n* [[Chat River]]\n* [[Ferr\u00e9e River (Ferr\u00e9 Lake)|Ferr\u00e9e River]]\n* [[Brisson River (Rimouski River tributary)|Brisson River]]\n* [[East Rimouski River]]\n}}\n\n=== Watershed of La Mitis and Eastern tributaries ===\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n* [[Mitis River]]\n** [[Neigette River (La Mitis)|Neigette River]]\n*** [[Little Neigette River]]\n**** [[Lunettes River]]\n*** [[Rouge River (Neigette River tributary)|Rouge River]]\n*** [[Paquet River]]\n*** [[Noire River (Neigette River tributary)|Noire River]]\n** [[Mistigoug\u00e8che River]]\n*** [[Ferr\u00e9e River (lac des Eaux Mortes)|Ferr\u00e9e River]]\n*** [[Armand-Leli\u00e8vre River]]\n** [[Mercier River]]\n** [[Saint-Pierre River (Mitis River tributary)|Saint-Pierre River]]\n** [[Rouge River (Mitis River tributary)|Rouge River]]\n* [[Tartigou River]]\n* [[Blanche River (Matane Township)|Blanche River]]\n** [[Alex River (Blanche River)]]\n** [[South Blanche River (Matane Township)|South Blanche River]]\n* [[Little Blanche River (Matane Township)|Little Blanche River]]\n* [[Matane River]]\n** [[Petchedetz River]]\n*** [[East Petchedetz River]]\n**** [[South Petchedetz River]]\n** [[Towagodi River]]\n** [[Tamagodi River]]\n** [[Rivi\u00e8re \u00e0 la Truite (Matane River tributary)|Rivi\u00e8re \u00e0 la Truite]] (Troot River)\n*** [[Petite Rivi\u00e8re \u00e0 la Truite (Rivi\u00e8re \u00e0 la Truite)|Petite Rivi\u00e8re \u00e0 la Truite]] (Little Troot River)\n** [[Rivi\u00e8re Bonjour]]\n** [[Duvivier River]]\n** [[Little Matane River]]\n}}\n\n=== Northern slope of Gasp\u00e9sie ===\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n* [[Pierre River (Les M\u00e9chins)|Pierre River]]\n* [[Rivi\u00e8re des Grands M\u00e9chins]] (Grand Mechins River)\n** [[Rivi\u00e8re des Grands M\u00e9chins Ouest]] (West Grand Mechins River)\n* [[Rivi\u00e8re des Grands Capucins]] (Grand Capucins River)\n* [[Cap-Chat River]]\n** [[Little Cap-Chat River]]\n*** [[Petite Rivi\u00e8re Cap-Chat Est]] (East Little Cap-Chat River)\n** [[Rivi\u00e8re Cap-Chat Est]] (East Cap-Chat River)\n* [[Sainte-Anne River (La Haute-Gasp\u00e9sie)|Sainte-Anne River]]\n** [[North-East Sainte-Anne River]]\n* [[Little Sainte-Anne River (La Haute-Gasp\u00e9sie)|Little Sainte-Anne River]]\n* [[Rivi\u00e8re \u00e0 la Martre (La Haute-Gasp\u00e9sie)|Rivi\u00e8re \u00e0 la Martre]]\n** [[Rivi\u00e8re \u00e0 la Martre Ouest (La Haute-Gasp\u00e9sie)|Rivi\u00e8re \u00e0 la Martre Ouest]]\n* [[Marsoui River]]\n** [[East Marsoui River]]\n* [[Claude River]]\n* [[Mont-Saint-Pierre River]]\n** [[East Branch (Mont-Saint-Pierre River tributary)|East Branch]]\n* [[Mont-Louis River]]\n** [[West Mont-Louis River]]\n* [[Anse Pleureuse River]]\n* [[Gros-Morne River]]\n* [[Manche d'\u00c9p\u00e9e River]]\n* [[Little River Madeleine (La Haute-Gasp\u00e9sie)|Little River Madeleine]]\n* [[Madeleine River (La Haute-Gasp\u00e9sie)|Madeleine River]]\n** [[South Madeleine River (Madeleine River tributary)|South Madeleine River]]\n** [[North Madeleine River (Madeleine River tributary)|North Madeleine River]]\n** [[B\u00e9land River (Madeleine River tributary)|B\u00e9land River]]\n** [[Diable River (Madeleine River tributary)|Diable River]]\n** [[Rivi\u00e8re \u00e0 l'Eau Claire (Madeleine River tributary)|Rivi\u00e8re \u00e0 l'Eau Claire]] (Clearwater River (Madeleine River)\n* [[Grande Vall\u00e9e River]]\n* [[Petite Vall\u00e9e River]]\n* [[Grand-Cloridorme River]]\n* [[Petit-Cloridorme River]]\n* [[Petite Rivi\u00e8re au Renard]] (Little Fox River)\n* [[Rivi\u00e8re au Renard (Gasp\u00e9)|Rivi\u00e8re au Renard]] (Fox River (Gasp\u00e9))\n** [[Morris River]]\n** [[Division River]]\n* [[Rivi\u00e8re de l'Anse au Griffon]] (Griffon Cove River)\n}}\n\n=== Watershed of Gasp\u00e9 Bay ===\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n* [[Dartmouth River]]\n** [[Little Fork River (Dartmouth River tributary)|Little Fork River]]\n* [[York River (Gasp\u00e9)|York River]]\n** [[Mississippi River (Gasp\u00e9)|Mississippi River]]\n** [[West Mississippi River (Gasp\u00e9)|West Mississippi River]]\n** [[La Petite Fourche (York River tributary)|La Petite Fourche]] (Little Fork)\n** [[La Grande Fourche (York River tributary)|La Grande Fourche]] (Grand Fork)\n* [[Saint-Jean River (Gasp\u00e9)|Saint-Jean River]]\n** [[South Saint-Jean River]]\n** [[West Saint-Jean River]]\n*[[Seal Cove River]]\n*[[Rivi\u00e8re de l'Anse \u00e0 Brillant]] (Brillant Cove River)\n}}\n\n=== Watershed of La Malbaie River (Perc\u00e9) ===\n* [[Malbaie River (Perc\u00e9)|Malbaie River]]\n** [[La Petite Fourche (Malbaie River tributary)|La Petite Fourche]]\n** [[La Grande Fourche (Malbaie River tributary)|La Grande Fourche]]\n* [[Beattie River]]\n* [[Portage River (Perc\u00e9)|Portage River]]\n* [[Murphy River (Perc\u00e9)|Murphy River]]\n\n=== Watershed of Chaleur Bay (east of Bonaventure River) ===\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n*[[Anse \u00e0 Beaufils River]]\n*[[Br\u00e8che \u00e0 Manon River]]\n*[[Grande Rivi\u00e8re (Perc\u00e9)|Grande Rivi\u00e8re]]\n**[[Gagnon River]]\n**[[Grande Rivi\u00e8re Est (Perc\u00e9)|Grande Rivi\u00e8re Est]]\n***[[Nadeau River]]\n** [[Grande Rivi\u00e8re Nord (Perc\u00e9)|Grande Rivi\u00e8re Nord]]\n** [[Grande Rivi\u00e8re Ouest (Perc\u00e9)|Grande Rivi\u00e8re Ouest]]\n*[[Petit Pabos River]]\n*[[Grand Pabos River]]\n**[[S\u00e8che River (Great Pabos River tributary)|S\u00e8che River]]\n**[[South Great Pabos River]]\n*[[Grand Pabos West River]]\n*[[Anse aux Canards River]]\n*[[Anse \u00e0 la Barbe River]]\n*[[Port-Daniel River]]\n*[[Port-Daniel du Milieu River]]\n*[[Little Port-Daniel River]]\n*[[Shigawake River]]\n*[[Saint-Godefroi River]]\n**[[Eusebe River]]\n*[[Paspebiac River]]\n}}\n\n=== Watershed of Chaleur Bay (west of Bonaventure River) ===\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n*[[Bonaventure River]]\n**[[Hall River (Bonaventure River tributary)|Hall River]]\n***[[West Hall River (Bonaventure River tributary)|West Hall River]]\n**[[Duval River]]\n**[[Garin River]]\n**[[Reboul River]]\n***[[North Reboul River]]\n**[[West Bonaventure River]]\n**[[La Petite Ouest (rivi\u00e8re)|La Petite Ouest]]\n*[[Saint-Sim\u00e9on River (Chaleur Bay)|Saint-Sim\u00e9on River]]\n*[[Caplan River]]\n*[[Little Cascap\u00e9dia River]]\n**[[Nouvelle River (Little Cascap\u00e9dia River tributary)|Nouvelle River]]\n**[[Little East Cascap\u00e9dia River]]\n**[[Little West Cascap\u00e9dia River]]\n**[[Rivi\u00e8re \u00e0 l'Oie (Little Cascap\u00e9dia River tributary)|Rivi\u00e8re \u00e0 l'Oie]]\n*[[Cascap\u00e9dia River]]\n**[[Ruisseau aux Saumons (Cascap\u00e9dia River tributary)|Ruisseau aux Saumons]]\n**[[Rivi\u00e8re Branche du Lac (Cascap\u00e9dia River tributary)|Rivi\u00e8re Branche du Lac]]\n**[[Square Forks River]]\n**[[Angers River]]\n***[[Ruisseau Grand Nord (Angers River tributary)|Ruisseau Grand Nord]]\n***[[South Angers River]]\n* [[Green River (Maria)|Green River]]\n* [[Stewart River (Quebec)|Stewart River]]\n**