on River, Vermont|Barton River]] (Vermont, United States)\n**** [[Willoughby River]] (Vermont, United States)\n***** [[Brownington Branch (Willoughby River tributary)|Brownington Branch]] (Vermont, United States)\n*** [[Clyde River (Vermont)|Clyde River]] (Vermont, United States)\n**** [[Pherrins River, Vermont]] (Vermont, United States)\n}}\n'''South bank of Saint-Fran\u00e7ois River'''\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n* [[Massawippi River]]\n** [[Coaticook River]]\n** [[Saumons River (Massawippi River tributary)|Saumons River]]\n*** [[Moe River]]\n** [[Lake Massawippi]]\n*** [[Tomifobia River]]\n**** [[Niger River]]\n* [[Eaton River]]\n** [[Clifton River]]\n** [[Eaton River North]]\n*** [[Newport River (Eaton River North)|Newport River]]\n* [[Saumon River (Le Haut-Saint-Fran\u00e7ois)|Saumon River]]\n** [[Chesham River]]\n** [[Ditton River]]\n*** [[Ditton River West]]\n*** [[Ditton River East]]\n* [[Rat River (Weedon)|Rat River]]\n* [[Bernier River (Saint-Fran\u00e7ois River tributary)|Bernier River]]\n}}\n'''North bank of Saint-Fran\u00e7ois River'''\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n* [[Moose River (Qu\u00e9bec)|Moose River]]\n* [[Coulombe River]]\n** [[Coulombe River North]]\n* [[Canard River]]\n* [[Weedon River]]\n* [[Bogue River]]\n}}\n'''[[Great Lake Saint-Fran\u00e7ois]]'''\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n* [[Felton River]]\n** [[Sauvage River (Felton River tributary)|Sauvage River]]\n** [[Noire River (Felton River tributary)|Noire River]]\n** [[Blanche River (Felton River tributary)|Blanche River]]\n** [[Legendre River (Felton River tributary)|Legendre River]]\n* [[Little River (lake Saint-Fran\u00e7ois)|Little River]]\n* [[Blueberries River (lake Saint-Fran\u00e7ois)|Blueberries River]]\n** [[Blueberries River South]]\n* [[Little Muskrat River]]\n* [[Muskrat River (Qu\u00e9bec)|Muskrat River]]\n* [[Or River]]\n* [[Ashberham River]]\n}}\n'''Lake Noir (Saint-Fran\u00e7ois River)'''\n* [[Bisby River]]\n* [[Coleraine River]]\n\n'''East bank of [[Saint-Fran\u00e7