reviation        = OZVA\n| motto               = \n| formation           = December 1993; {{Years or months ago|1993|12}}\n| type                = Sport organisation\n| headquarters        = \n| region_served       = [[Oceania]]\n| membership          = 20 member associations\n| language            = [[English language|English]] \n| leader_title        = President\n| leader_name         = {{flagdeco|COK}} Hugh Graham\n| parent_organization = [[Asian Volleyball Confederation|AVC]]\n| website             = [http://oceaniavolleyball.org/ OceaniaVolleyball.org]\n}}\n\nThe '''Oceania Zonal Volleyball Association (OZVA)''', is the [[sports governing body|governing body]] for the [[sport]]s of [[volleyball|indoor]], [[beach volleyball|beach]] and grass [[volleyball]] in [[Oceania]].\n\nIn the spirit of the FIVB 2001 Plan, AVC was the first to create five Zonal Associations at the 10th General Assembly in December 1993 prior to the FIVB Centennial Congress in September 1994.\n\n==Members==\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable hlist\" style=\"text-align:center; font-size:100%;\"\n! {{tooltip|Code|FIVB country code}} !! Association !! National teams !! [[International Olympic Committee|IOC]]<br/>member !! [[Olympic Council of Asia|OCA]]<br/>member !! [[Oceania National Olympic Committees|ONOC]]<br/>member\n|-\n|ASA ||style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|ASA}} {{tooltip|American Samoa|American Samoa Volleyball Association}}||([[American Samoa men's national volleyball team|M]], [[American Samoa women's national volleyball team|W]])||{{yes}}||{{no}}||{{yes}}\n|-\n|AUS ||style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|AUS}} [[Australian Volleyball Federation|{{tooltip|Australia|Australian Volleyball Federation}}]]||([[Australia men's national volleyball team|M]], [[Australia women's national volleyball team|W]])||{{yes}}||{{no}}||{{yes}}\n|-\n|COK ||style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|COK}} {{tooltip|Cook Islands|Cook Islands Volleyball Association}}||([[Cook Islands men's national volleyball team|M]], [[Cook Islands women's national volleyball team|W]])||{{yes}}||{{no}}||{{yes}}\n|-\n|FIJ || style=\"text-align:left;\" |{{flagicon|FJI}} {{tooltip|Fiji|Fiji Volleyball Federation}}||([[Fiji men's national volleyball team|M]], [[Fiji women's national volleyball team|W]])||{{yes}}||{{no}}||{{yes}}\n|-\n|FSM ||style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|FSM}} {{tooltip|Federated States of Micronesia|Federated States of Micronesia Volleyball Association}}||([[Federated States of Micronesia men's national volleyball team|M]], [[Federated States of Micronesia women's national volleyball team|W]])||{{yes}}||{{no}}||{{yes}}\n|-\n|GUM ||style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|GUM}} {{tooltip|Guam|Guam Volleyball Federation}}||([[Guam men's national volleyball team|M]], [[Guam women's national volleyball team|W]])||{{yes}}||{{no}}||{{yes}}\n|-\n|KIR ||style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|KIR}} {{tooltip|Kiribati|Kiribati Volleyball Federation}}||([[Kiribati men's national volleyball team|M]], [[Kiribati women's national volleyball team|W]])||{{yes}}||{{no}}||{{yes}}\n|-\n|MHL ||style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|MHL}} {{tooltip|Marshall Islands|Republic of the Marshall Islands Volleyball Federation}}||([[Marshall Islands men's national volleyball team|M]], [[Marshall Islands women's national volleyball team|W]])||{{yes}}||{{no}}||{{yes}}\n|-\n|NMI || style=\"text-align:left;\" |{{flagicon|MNP}} [http://www.nmivolleyball.org {{tooltip|Northern Mariana|Northern Mariana Islands Volleyball Association}}]||([[Northern Mariana men's national volleyball team|M]], [[Northern Mariana women's national volleyball team|W]])||{{no}}||{{no}}||{{yes}}\n|-\n|NIU ||style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|NIU}} {{tooltip|Niue|Niue Island Volleyball Association}}||([[Niue men's national volleyball team|M]], [[Niue women's national volleyball team|W]])||{{no}}||{{no}}||{{yes}}\n|-\n|NRU ||style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|NRU}} {{tooltip|Nauru|Nauru Volleyball Association}}||([[Nauru men's national volleyball team|M]], [[Nauru women's national volleyball team|W]])||{{yes}}||{{no}}||{{yes}}\n|-\n|NZL ||style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|NZL}} {{tooltip|New Zealand|Volleyball New Zealand}}||([[New Zealand men's national volleyball team|M]], [[New Zealand women's national volleyball team|W]])||{{yes}}||{{no}}||{{yes}}\n|-\n|PAU || style=\"text-align:left;\" |{{flagicon|PLW}} {{tooltip|Palau|Palau Amateur Volleyball Association}}||([[Palau men's national volleyball team|M]], [[Palau women's national volleyball team|W]])||{{yes}}||{{no}}||{{yes}}\n|-\n|PLY ||style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|TAH}} {{tooltip|French Polynesia|Volleyball Federation of Tahiti}}||([[French Polynesia men's national volleyball team|M]], [[French Polynesia women's national volleyball team|W]])||{{no}}||{{no}}||{{yes}}\n|-\n|PNG ||style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|PNG}} {{tooltip|Papua New Guinea|Papua New Guinea Amateur Volleyball Federation}}||([[Papua New Guinea men's national volleyball team|M]], [[Papua New Guinea women's national volleyball team|W]])||{{yes}}||{{no}}||{{yes}}\n|-\n|SAM || style=\"text-align:left;\" |{{flagicon|WSM}} {{tooltip|Samoa|Western Samoa Volleyball Association}}||([[Samoa men's national volleyball team|M]], [[Samoa women's national volleyball team|W]])||{{yes}}||{{no}}||{{yes}}\n|-\n|SLM ||style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|SOL}} {{tooltip|Solomon Islands|Solomon Islands Volleyball Federation}}||([[Solomon Islands men's national volleyball team|M]], [[Solomon Islands women's national volleyball team|W]])||{{yes}}||{{no}}||{{yes}}\n|-\n|TGA || style=\"text-align:left;\" |{{flagicon|TON}} {{tooltip|Tonga Islands|Tonga National Volleyball Association}}||([[Tonga men's national volleyball team|M]], [[Tonga women's national volleyball team|W]])||{{yes}}||{{no}}||{{yes}}\n|-\n|TUV ||style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|TUV}} {{tooltip|Tuvalu|Federation De Volleyball De Tuvalu}}||([[Tuvalu men's national volleyball team|M]], [[Tuvalu women's national volleyball team|W]])||{{yes}}||{{no}}||{{yes}}\n|-\n|VUT ||style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|VUT}} {{tooltip|Vanuatu|Vanuatu Amateur Volleyball}}||([[Vanuatu men's national volleyball team|M]], [[Vanuatu women's national volleyball team|W]])||{{yes}}||{{no}}||{{yes}}\n|-\n|}\n\n==Ranking==\n{{Col-begin}}\n{{Col-1-of-2}}\n\n===Men's national teams===\n====Senior team====\nRankings are calculated by [[F\u00e9d\u00e9ration Internationale de Volleyball|FIVB]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.fivb.org/en/volleyball/VB_Ranking_U21_2015-09.asp|title=FIVB Men's U21 World Ranking \u2013 As per September 2015|publisher=FIVB}}</ref>\n\n{|class=\"wikitable\" cellpadding=\"1\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n!OZVA\n![[Asian Volleyball Confederation|AVC]]\n![[F\u00e9d\u00e9ration Internationale de Volleyball|FIVB]]\n!Country\n!Points\n!Change\n|-\n|1\n|3\n|15\n|align=left|{{vb|Australia}}\n|65\n|{{decrease}} 3\n|-\n|2\n|13\n|50\n|align=left|{{vb|New Zealand}}\n|10\n|{{increase}} 2\n|-\n|rowspan=3|3\n|rowspan=3|25\n|rowspan=3|137\n|align=left|{{vb|Fiji}}\n|rowspan=3|0\n|rowspan=3|{{steady}}\n|-\n|align=left|{{vb|Samoa}}\n|-\n|align=left|{{vb|Tonga}}\n|}\n[http://www.fivb.org/en/volleyball/VB_Ranking_M_2016-08.asp Last updated 22 August 2016]\n\n{{Col-2-of-2}}\n\n===Women's national teams===\n====Senior team====\nRankings are calculated by [[F\u00e9d\u00e9ration Internationale de Volleyball|FIVB]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.fivb.org/en/volleyball/VB_Ranking_U21_2015-09.asp|title=FIVB Men's U21 World Ranking \u2013 As per September 2015|publisher=FIVB}}</ref>\n\n{|class=\"wikitable\" cellpadding=\"1\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n!OZVA\n![[Asian Volleyball Confederation|AVC]]\n![[F\u00e9d\u00e9ration Internationale de Volleyball|FIVB]]\n!Country\n!Points\n!Change\n|-\n|1\n|6\n|43\n|align=left|{{vbw|Australia}}\n|11\n|{{steady}} \n|-\n|2\n|10\n|64\n|align=left|{{vbw|New Zealand}}\n|8\n|{{decrease}} 2\n|-\n|rowspan=3|3\n|rowspan=3|15\n|rowspan=3|115\n|align=le